#ROOM
Vnum     41200
Name     &rThe Obsidian Archway&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The humid air of Dustwallow Marsh is left behind as you step 
through the massive, jagged entrance of Onyxia's Lair. The air 
here is an absolute furnace, and the walls are composed of 
solid black glass. A long, descending tunnel of obsidian leads 
deep into the heart of the mountain.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    37590
Desc      Return to the surface of Dustwallow Marsh.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    41201
Desc      The descending corridor.~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41201
Name     &rThe Searing Descent&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide thoroughfare built for the passage of dragons. The 
ground is hot to the touch, and the air carries the scent of 
sulfur and ancient scales. Onyxian warders stand in alcoves 
along the walls, watching for intruders.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    41202
Desc      The crossroads of fire.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41200
Desc      The entrance archway.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 41002 10 41201
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41202
Name     &rThe Crossroads of Fire&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The main tunnel splits here. To the west lies the Scorched 
Hatchery, where the next generation of the flight is 
prepared. To the east, a wide bridge crosses a river of 
magma toward the military quarters.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    41300
Desc      Toward the Broodmother's Hall.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    41250
Desc      Toward the Foundries.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41201
Desc      The entrance corridor.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    41203
Desc      Toward the Hatchery.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 41008 5 41202
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41203
Name     &rThe Scorched Hatchery - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The sound of thousands of tiny high-pitched screeches fills 
the air. The walls are covered in web-like dragon-silk, and 
the air is humid and smells of reptile musk. Hatchery 
assistants move about, inspecting the egg sacs.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    41204
Desc      The Egg Chambers.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    41202
Desc      The crossroads.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 41009 5 41203
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41204
Name     &rThe Egg Chambers - West&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive circular room filled with hundreds of obsidian eggs. 
Onyxian whelps play in the warm updrafts rising from 
floor vents, while technicians carefully maintain the 
temperature.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    41205
Desc      The Breeding Pit.~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41203
Desc      The hatchery entry.~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 41003 20 41204
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     41205
