Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The heart of the dragon-breeding operation. A massive 
black drake stands guard over a pool of magical fluid, 
ensuring the stability of the chromatic brood. The floor 
is littered with broken eggshells and bone.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    41204
Desc      The egg chambers.~
#ENDEXIT

